pricing_analysis.trend: Aggressive price competition is dramatically lowering token costs, driven by highly efficient mid-tier models like Gemini 1.5 Flash and DeepSeek V2. The $20/month subscription model has become the standard for premium consumer access (ChatGPT Plus, Claude Pro, Gemini Advanced). Open-source models, like Llama 3, are commoditizing high-end capabilities by offering zero licensing cost, shifting expenses to self-hosting or third-party cloud inference. Enterprise pricing remains highly customized, focusing on volume discounts and private deployment options.
